div.p: Dandrogram of major compounds (phenyl propanoids) in ACLEO and ACREO prepared Software SPSS, ward method with square Euclidean distance measure. Where 1 = spring, 2 = summer, 3 = autumn, 4 = winter seasons, L = A. calamus leaves essential oils (ALEO), R = A. calamus rhizomes essential oils (RLEO).
